      ],
      "parameters": {
        "width": 288,
        "height": 400,
        "content": "## How it works\n**Purpose:** Automate daily Meta Ads reporting for multiple clients. \n\n**Flow:** Read client config from Google Sheets → loop through clients → request campaign insights from Meta Ads API → split campaigns into rows → append to each client’s report sheet → send Telegram status message. \n\n**Inputs:** client_register sheet (ad_account_id, access_token, report_sheet_url). \n\n**Outputs:** campaign-level rows in Google Sheets + Telegram notification."
      },
      "typeVersion": 1
    },
